---
title: Turkey and Apple Burgers with Rosemary Potatoes and Mixed Green Salad
description: Turkey and apple are a match made in heaven! In this dish, they are combined into a juicy burger – and it can't get much better, but it does with roasted rosemary potatoes and a leafy side salad as the perfect accompaniments.
